  "notes": "Dadra and Nagar Haveli and Daman and Diu is a union territory in India formed on January 26, 2020, by merging the former union territories of Dadra and Nagar Haveli and Daman and Diu. It consists of 3 districts: Dadra and Nagar Haveli, Daman, and Diu. The territory comprises four separate geographical entities spread across the western coast of India."
